! $$scalarName For scalar entries!
! $vectorName  For vector entries!
!   Comments are in between two exclamation points !

!
Obs: in Step entries are vectors (X, Y, Z)
On the 3D case Step_mult could be for instance 0.5 0.1 1

the variables "*_initial" will overwrite the ones set in "mesh_input"
!

$$step_variate T
$step_initial 0.1 0.2 0.4
$step_mult 0.5 0.5 0.5
$step_add 0.0 0.0 0.0
$$step_nIter 3

$$nmc_variate F
$$nmc_initial 3
$$nmc_mult 10
$$nmc_add 0.0
$$nmc_nIter 4